- Launch with necessary configs
- install all software

- install certbot using nginx tutorial by running certbot extension for nginx ie using --nginx
flag during starting of certbot and setting server_name in sites-avail/defaults to the
dns attached to the certbot to enable auomatic configuration

- set prevent instance shotdown setiing on ec2 machine
- used CNAME dns record to point flexrecords.cloza.tech to public ec2 dns name
